    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Process used to reconstruct the three-dimensional structure of blood vessels by replacing the blood with low viscosity resin; the vascular architecture may then be removed from surrounding tissues.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
